<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-82-0264 </DOCNO><TEXT>A general formulation of quantum scattering theory for systems of threeparticles endowed with an internal structure is suggested. Modified Faddeevequations corresponding to a certain special class of energy-dependentinteractions are derived. properties of these equations are studied.</TEXT></DOC>